-DMG_DISABLE_HTTP_DIGEST_AUTH -DMG_DISABLE_MD5 -DMG_DISABLE_HTTP_KEEP_ALIVE 




When we add the aforementioned mongoose.c to the build and add the needed flags to CFLAGS , the project will compile.

we'll need a bit more of the heap memory. By default, it's 512 bytes; for this example, we'll need at least 1024. 
It is defined as a preprocessor macro __HEAP_SIZE .
